<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <script src="js/jquery-2.1.3.js"></script>
    <script src="js/jqmobile/jquery.mobile-1.4.5.min.js"></script>
    <script src="js/knockout-3.3.0.js"></script>
    <script src="js/demo.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/styles.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="js/jqmobile/jquery.mobile-1.4.5.min.css">
    <title>Reptile IO</title>
  </head>
  <body id="app">
    <!--img data-bind="attr: {src: imgSrc}"/-->
    <div data-role="page">
      <div data-role="header">
        <h1>Nock Nock!</h1>
      </div>
      <div id="content" data-role="content">
        <div id="events-container" data-bind="foreach: events">
          <img data-bind="attr: {src: imgSrc}, visible: show"/>
          <div data-bind="text: date, visible: show"></div>
        </div>
        <div data-role="fieldcontain">
          <label for="slider-time"><strong>Last X minutes: </strong></label>
          <input type="range" name="slider-time" id="slider-time" value="30" min="0" max="30" step="1"/>  
        </div>
        <br>
        <p>The UVB light is set to turn off at 10pm and turn back on at 7am. To give the chameleon fresh water, water will be squirted onto the plant every 6 hours.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
